'''Ron Morgan''' (born May 25, 1951) is a [[Canada|Canadian]] former professional [[ice hockey]] player. 

During the [[1973–74 WHA season|1973–74]] season, Morgan played four games in the [[World Hockey Association]] with the [[Cleveland Crusaders]].<ref>https://www.hockey-reference.com/players/m/morgaro01.html</ref>

